    <item>
      <title>埃及总统塞西拒绝特朗普要求驱逐加沙巴勒斯坦人的呼吁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/egypt-can-t-play-role-in-displacing-palestinians-el-sisi-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普建议将加沙地带的居民迁移至埃及和约旦，埃及总统阿卜杜勒·法塔赫·塞西表示，埃及不能参与强制巴勒斯坦人迁出加沙的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/egypt-can-t-play-role-in-displacing-palestinians-el-sisi-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 15:01:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>谢恩鲍姆预计特朗普不会在 2 月 1 日征收 25% 的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/mexico-s-sheinbaum-doesn-t-expect-trump-s-25-tariffs-on-feb-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·谢因鲍姆（Claudia Sheinbaum）没有回答有关墨西哥是否预计美国总统唐纳德·特朗普将于 2 月 1 日宣布对墨西哥商品征收 25% 关税的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/mexico-s-sheinbaum-doesn-t-expect-trump-s-25-tariffs-on-feb-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 15:00:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前参议员鲍勃·梅内德斯就金条案请求宽恕</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/disgraced-ex-senator-menendez-pleads-for-mercy-in-gold-bar-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法官将在对鲍勃·梅内德斯进行量刑时，权衡这位前参议员半个世纪以来的公共服务与检察官提出的判处其 15 年监禁的要求，此前，梅内德斯因系统性地利用职权谋取私利而被定罪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/disgraced-ex-senator-menendez-pleads-for-mercy-in-gold-bar-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯要求希思罗机场修建“急需”的第三条跑道</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/uk-supports-third-runway-at-heathrow-airport-reeves-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 全力支持修建备受争议的希思罗机场第三条跑道，这是工党政府为重振经济增长而做出的努力之一，她批准了长期被推迟的基础设施项目。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/uk-supports-third-runway-at-heathrow-airport-reeves-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 10:51:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢特尼克承诺出任商务部长，出售“一切”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/lutnick-pledges-to-be-responsive-to-business-as-commerce-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普提名的商务部长霍华德·卢特尼克表示，如果获得确认，他计划出售其所有资产和商业利益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/lutnick-pledges-to-be-responsive-to-business-as-commerce-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普瞄准援助，哈佛、耶鲁做好应对资金风险的准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/harvard-u-chicago-caution-faculty-as-schools-weigh-trump-order</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普的代理预算主管发布了一份全面的备忘录，指示各机构暂停联邦财政拨款和贷款，同时政府审查支出是否符合最近的行政命令。此后，美国各大学正在为可能出现的资金中断做准备，尤其是用于科学研究的资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/harvard-u-chicago-caution-faculty-as-schools-weigh-trump-order</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 00:06:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
